        <h6 class="content-title">Minecraft Rules!</h6>
        <p>
         - No toxicity, NSFW Content, Swearing, Racism, Causing Drama, Spamming or posting links in the game chat (Also English only in the chat!)
         <br>
         - Don't grief other people's builds
         <br>
         - Don't take anything without permission from the owner of the build
         <br>
         - Don't kill others pets that are clearly pets
         <br>
         - Treat others with respect. There's no need to say or do things to make others feel bad or upset
         <br>
         - No  begging for in-game items/ranks etc.
         <br>
         - Let staff do there jobs, if they need to fix a grief or something like that, don't do it yourself
         <br>
         - Don't hack or use any mods that will give any advantages over other players.
         <br> 
         If you are unsure what mods are allowed, ask in the <a href="https://discord.gg/XgjhUU92FN">Discord</a>
